OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FThe King's speech has outlined the
OL,7,FGovernment's plans for the next year,
OL,8,Fwhich include making the plotting of
OL,9,FSouthport-style mass casualties a
OL,10,Fspecific criminal offence.
OL,12,FIt also reiterated plans for a
OL,13,FHillsborough Law to force public
OL,14,Fbodies to tell the truth and end a
OL,15,Fculture of cover-ups.
OL,17,FThe Northern Powerhouse Rail bill
OL,18,Fincluded a new high-speed route
OL,19,Fbetween Liverpool and Manchester via
OL,20,FWarrington and Manchester Airport.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FAs well as the promise of better cross-
OL,7,FPennine links, over and above the
OL,8,Fimprovements that are already under
OL,9,Fway.
OL,11,FBut the speech was overshadowed by the
OL,12,Funcertainty over the Prime Minister's
OL,13,Ffuture and whether a leadership
OL,14,Fchallenge would include the Greater
OL,15,FManchester mayor Andy Burnham.
OL,17,FWe asked some of our North West MPs
OL,18,Fwhether what they'd heard was enough
OL,19,Fto secure Sir Keir Starmer's future?
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FLabour MP for Liverpool West Derby,
OL,7,FIan Byrne, says it's too little too
OL,8,Flate: "I feel sorry for the country,
OL,9,Fand I just think that so many bad
OL,10,Fdecisions are being made. He hasn't
OL,11,Fshown the leadership required for me."
OL,13,F"We've got 1000s of people in West
OL,14,FDerby living in poverty that thought
OL,15,Fwe were going to get a change, and
OL,16,Fthat's reflected across the country."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FBut the Labour MP for Bolton West,
OL,7,FPhil Brickell, says he saw a 'really
OL,8,Fambitious and bold' agenda set out: "I
OL,9,Fthink it builds on what we've already
OL,10,Fseen in the first session of
OL,11,FParliament, 50 bills that managed to
OL,12,Fget through, including some really
OL,13,Fambitious reforms that are now in
OL,14,Fplace.
OL,16,F"We've already seen the biggest roll
OL,17,Fout of employment rights in a
OL,18,Fgeneration, but also around protection
OL,19,Ffor renters, to make sure that they
OL,20,Fcan't get kicked out by unscrupulous
OL,21,Flandlords.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,F"I think this is an ambitious
OL,7,Fprogramme for government, and I'm
OL,8,Ffocused on making sure that we can
OL,9,Fdeliver it successfully over the next
OL,10,Fyear."
OL,12,FAlso watching closely was the Reform
OL,13,FUK MP for Runcorn and Helsby, Sarah
OL,14,FPochin.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FShe said it was 'overwhelming' to
OL,7,Fwatch her first Kings Speech: "It
OL,8,Factually brought a little tear to my
OL,9,Feye, because I couldn't believe how
OL,10,Fprivileged I was to actually be there
OL,11,F- something I'd watched for years on
OL,12,Fthe television, and then to be
OL,13,Fstanding there in the chamber was
OL,14,Fcompletely overwhelming."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1778767871
OL,3,CMPs react to the King's Speech as PM
OL,4,Cfights to keep his job
OL,6,FBut she was underwhelmed by its
OL,7,Fcontent: "It focused on energy,
OL,8,Ffocused on business and focused on
OL,9,Fdefence. Those were his three key
OL,10,Fmessages I picked up. And that is
OL,11,Fexactly the policy areas where
OL,12,FReformers say this government is
OL,13,Ffailing the country so badly."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
